{"tid":2031801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽：中港評級相去不遠","createTime":"2020-05-23T15:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T16:29:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ec9f736f05c7b85105b9f07cd7f6035f4fe3ab","tid":2031801,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200523/ZB3X5GHX5XTNYPHMLTFE6GTM5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200523%2FZB3X5GHX5XTNYPHMLTFE6GTM5E%2F&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d3ad09f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200523%2FZB3X5GHX5XTNYPHMLTFE6GTM5E%2F&h=53e703b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200523/ZB3X5GHX5XTNYPHMLTFE6GTM5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n惠譽：中港評級相去不遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200523/large/1590167458_6242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200523%2Flarge%2F1590167458_6242.jpg&h=06e64fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n惠譽指中國和香港的評級只有一個等級的差距，反映香港逐漸融入中國國家治理體系。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「港版國安法」將直接於香港實施，評級機構惠譽亞太區主權評級高級董事費安德（Andrew Fennell）昨回覆本報查詢表示，香港分別於去年9月及今年4月被降級，中國和香港的評級只有一個等級的差距，反映香港逐漸融入中國國家治理體系。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭避答會否交大陸審訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反映漸融入中國治理體系<br />\n<br />\n費安德昨向本報稱，惠譽過去一年內兩度調低香港主權信貸評級，當中最近一次是今年4月20日，該行將香港主權信貸評級從「AA」降至「AA-」，展..................................<br />\n<br />\n目前中國與香港信貸評級僅相差一個等級，惠譽相信足以反...............................<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自去年初港府提出《逃犯條例》修例，引起本地社會強烈反響，觸發..................................<br />\n<br />\n惠譽去年9月將香港主權評級，由「AA+」降至「AA」，展望為..........................<br />\n<br />\n惠譽於報告提到，料香港可維持「一國兩制」框架不變，但香港...........................<br />\n<br />\n穆迪則於今年1月初調低香港主權信貸評級，由「Aa2」降至「Aa3」，展望為負面。穆迪分析指香港沒有展現具體計劃處理香港市民所反映的政治、經濟以及................................"},{"pid":"759837bbb60aca054b4dec116e5363fc91268c44","tid":2031801,"uid":4942,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:00:47.000Z","msg":"......................."},{"pid":"c547e25000547efb95a0d40d8666af587bd8759f","tid":2031801,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"快啦 唔好淨係講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d28930142b0cbfa9dd4750cb6a7e4f415a354fd","tid":2031801,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c547e25000547efb95a0d40d8666af587bd8759f","tid":2031801,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"快啦 唔好淨係講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"未表決所以仲未降級？"},{"pid":"a5710f010aa7dee5d6d0f9511bbf94e937db0aea","tid":2031801,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"B+未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e247c1e5f648d8737aecbe8bacb69a08041c63de","tid":2031801,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"穆迪分析指香港沒有展現具體計劃處理香港市民所反映的政治、經濟以及社會問題，本港管治能力不及該行原先評估，也可能是本港自治權較原先估計有更大限制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個帶頭攬炒 評級機構真係睇得好透好準<br />\n<br />\n柒娥份香港的真相簡直世界笑料"},{"pid":"4f3005b51a83d797b33bfce86dd62f821371b3e1","tid":2031801,"uid":128923,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:06:51.000Z","msg":"聲明<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n絕不同意，不認同惠譽<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"5088cf1884c0e6ec05c1d39a7144dfaf22ef62c2","tid":2031801,"uid":15815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"喂公平咩<br />\n香港有d區跌到深圳樓價先啱數喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"h